WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.310
I just want to

00:00:02.320 --> 00:00:05.630
tell you all that I feel uplifted in my

00:00:05.640 --> 00:00:08.310
spirit. You can just feel

00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:10.509
the spiritual charge that is

00:00:10.519 --> 00:00:12.870
taking place in the atmosphere with all

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:15.030
these people that are praying.

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:16.590
If one of us can put a thousand to

00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:18.630
flight and two of us can send 10,000 to

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:23.509
flight, think about how many thousands of

00:00:23.519 --> 00:00:26.390
us sending into flight the power and the authority.

00:00:26.390 --> 00:00:26.400
There is

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:29.589
nothing that the

00:00:29.599 --> 00:00:33.229
Lord can't do through us

00:00:33.239 --> 00:00:36.350
if we just act in simple faith,

00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:39.910
believe, pray, and be that

00:00:39.910 --> 00:00:39.920
army—that

00:00:39.920 --> 00:00:42.750
body joined together. I'm telling you, we are

00:00:42.750 --> 00:00:42.760
about to see

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:45.150
one of the greatest harvests of souls

00:00:45.160 --> 00:00:46.990
this world has ever seen.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:48.869
I want you all to agree with

00:00:48.879 --> 00:00:51.470
me: take the blinders off of people's

00:00:51.480 --> 00:00:54.990
eyes. A spiritual awakening, a spiritual

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:57.510
outpouring of the Spirit of God like

00:00:57.520 --> 00:01:00.430
we've never seen before—the waking

00:01:00.430 --> 00:01:00.440
from

00:01:00.440 --> 00:01:03.349
the slumber of the

00:01:03.349 --> 00:01:03.359
seeker-friendlies

00:01:03.359 --> 00:01:07.149
and the people who are asleep

00:01:07.159 --> 00:01:09.870
spiritually. Praying for their eyes to be

00:01:09.880 --> 00:01:12.350
enlightened, praying for the

00:01:12.360 --> 00:01:14.429
demonstrations and the manifestations

00:01:14.439 --> 00:01:16.510
not just to happen in a couple of

00:01:16.520 --> 00:01:19.590
churches, but in all the churches.

00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:21.590
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, it

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:23.670
won't just be the Pentecostals, it won't

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:26.630
just be the charismatics.

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:30.149
It will be the body of Christ.'It

00:01:30.149 --> 00:01:30.159
won't be

00:01:30.159 --> 00:01:32.870
just one

00:01:32.870 --> 00:01:32.880
denomination—like

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:35.870
the Word of Faith bunch that is on

00:01:35.880 --> 00:01:38.190
fire for the Lord. We stand

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:39.749
and we know how to live by faith, we know

00:01:39.759 --> 00:01:41.550
how to live by the Word of God, and we stand

00:01:41.560 --> 00:01:43.870
on the Word of God, but there are still a

00:01:43.880 --> 00:01:46.590
lot of people that walk in defeat. I

00:01:46.600 --> 00:01:49.709
am ready to stop playing church.

00:01:49.719 --> 00:01:53.590
I am tired of going to church

00:01:53.590 --> 00:01:53.600
and

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:56.749
not

00:01:56.759 --> 00:01:59.310
getting anything—I want that tangible

00:01:59.320 --> 00:02:02.029
presence of God to the point where

00:02:02.039 --> 00:02:05.469
you walk away changed. I don't want to

00:02:05.479 --> 00:02:10.110
live where I was five days ago. I want to

00:02:10.120 --> 00:02:12.589
live exceedingly abundantly above all

00:02:12.599 --> 00:02:14.070
that I dare ask or think. People say,

00:02:14.070 --> 00:02:14.080
'Well,

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:15.710
you had another visit from

00:02:15.710 --> 00:02:15.720
Jesus?'Yes,

00:02:15.720 --> 00:02:20.430
I expect it. I expect Him to show up.

00:02:20.440 --> 00:02:22.589
I expect to have a relationship with the

00:02:22.599 --> 00:02:25.910
Father; He is my Father. It

00:02:25.920 --> 00:02:27.949
shouldn't be out of the ordinary to

00:02:27.959 --> 00:02:30.790
have a visitation from the Lord, to

00:02:30.800 --> 00:02:33.190
have demonstrations and manifestations.

00:02:33.200 --> 00:02:35.229
He said greater works would we do. He

00:02:35.239 --> 00:02:36.830
said you would lay hands on the sick and

00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:38.470
they would recover. You would cast out

00:02:38.480 --> 00:02:40.990
devils, bring

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:43.509
sight to the blind, and raise the dead. He

00:02:43.519 --> 00:02:46.070
told us we would do this.

00:02:46.080 --> 00:02:47.710
What's amazing, folks, is that's

00:02:47.710 --> 00:02:47.720
not

00:02:47.720 --> 00:02:49.350
supposed to be special; that's

00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:51.589
just the Great Commission. He

00:02:51.599 --> 00:02:53.550
commissioned every single one of us to

00:02:53.560 --> 00:02:55.869
walk in that authority. He commissioned

00:02:55.879 --> 00:02:57.550
every single

00:02:57.560 --> 00:03:01.390
believer. So what does that say? A child

00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:04.390
has the authority to cast out a devil. A

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:06.630
child has authority to lay hands on the

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:09.910
sick and see them recover. It

00:03:09.920 --> 00:03:12.430
didn't say a 'seasoned veteran believer';

00:03:12.440 --> 00:03:16.509
he said 'believers,'if you believe. So we

00:03:16.519 --> 00:03:18.589
always feel, 'No, that's for

00:03:18.599 --> 00:03:20.589
Brother Brandon,'or, 'No, that's

00:03:20.599 --> 00:03:22.830
for Sister Billy; she's a teacher and God equipped her.'No, that's for

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:30.390
you, ladies and gentlemen.

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:32.949
He gave you power. He didn't give

00:03:32.959 --> 00:03:35.589
anybody else special treatment; He is no

00:03:35.589 --> 00:03:35.599
respecter

00:03:35.599 --> 00:03:37.949
of persons. I want you to

00:03:37.959 --> 00:03:41.470
be encouraged that you have that

00:03:41.480 --> 00:03:44.869
ability the moment you accept Jesus

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:47.190
Christ as your Lord and personal Savior.

00:03:47.200 --> 00:03:48.990
You are seated with Him in the

00:03:48.990 --> 00:03:49.000
heavenlies,

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:51.149
far above all principalities, powers,

00:03:51.159 --> 00:03:53.630
and might. I'm trying to emphasize

00:03:53.640 --> 00:03:55.910
how important it is for you to

00:03:55.920 --> 00:03:58.190
understand who He is and that He lives

00:03:58.200 --> 00:04:01.190
in you—Christ in you. So, I just want to

00:04:01.200 --> 00:04:03.830
encourage you all today.

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:06.190
We're going to pray over

00:04:06.200 --> 00:04:08.869
your situations and your

00:04:08.869 --> 00:04:08.879
households.

00:04:08.879 --> 00:04:10.309
I'll just

00:04:10.319 --> 00:04:11.589
pray in the Spirit with you for a

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:14.830
little bit and attach my faith with

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:17.229
yours for your finances, for an

00:04:17.239 --> 00:04:19.349
outpouring of finances. I'm believing God

00:04:19.359 --> 00:04:22.710
for cryptos and for big

00:04:22.710 --> 00:04:22.720
things—gold,

00:04:22.720 --> 00:04:24.629
silver, and things like that—that God

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:26.629
would turn things around and give us witty

00:04:26.639 --> 00:04:28.870
ideas to get wealth. God will give

00:04:28.880 --> 00:04:30.510
you

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:34.790
a surplus. I'm not just believing for

00:04:34.790 --> 00:04:34.800
your

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:37.310
food to be taken care of

00:04:37.320 --> 00:04:40.590
today, but for having more

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:41.990
than enough to be able to help your

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:44.150
neighbor, a loved one,

00:04:44.150 --> 00:04:44.160
or

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:47.110
someone

00:04:47.110 --> 00:04:47.120
else.

00:04:47.120 --> 00:04:50.550
Believe

00:04:50.560 --> 00:04:53.189
Him for overflow to take care of

00:04:53.199 --> 00:04:54.990
other people

00:04:54.990 --> 00:04:55.000
besides

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:57.749
yourself. It's time to believe God for

00:04:57.759 --> 00:05:00.230
big. It's time to believe God for

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:02.110
exceedingly abundantly above all that we

00:05:02.120 --> 00:05:04.189
dare ask or think—to believe Him for the

00:05:04.199 --> 00:05:06.670
big thing. That's where I believe we are:

00:05:09.280 --> 00:05:12.990
believing God for abundance. So let's

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:16.270
believe Him today. Father, we

00:05:16.280 --> 00:05:18.110
thank you right now in the name of

00:05:18.120 --> 00:05:22.950
Jesus. We speak to the mountain of debt,

00:05:22.960 --> 00:05:25.990
we speak to the mountain of poverty, and

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:28.309
we command it to bow its knee in the

00:05:28.319 --> 00:05:31.430
name of Jesus and be cast into the sea.

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:33.270
Father, I thank you that we have

00:05:33.280 --> 00:05:35.230
authority over debt

00:05:35.230 --> 00:05:35.240
and

00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:37.830
poverty. We speak to

00:05:37.840 --> 00:05:40.110
lack and 'not

00:05:40.110 --> 00:05:40.120
enough'and

00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:43.189
barely getting by, and we say: no

00:05:43.199 --> 00:05:48.790
more. We have abundance, we have overflow,

00:05:48.790 --> 00:05:48.800
and

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:51.550
we have more than enough in the name of

00:05:51.560 --> 00:05:54.990
Jesus. Thank you, Father,

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:57.550
for overflow and for

00:05:57.560 --> 00:05:59.430
exceedingly abundantly above all that we

00:05:59.440 --> 00:06:00.990
dare ask or

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:03.629
think. Thank you, Father, that you've

00:06:03.639 --> 00:06:06.790
made a way for them not just to

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:09.749
live paycheck to paycheck, but to live

00:06:11.240 --> 00:06:13.710
lavishly. God wants to let you live

00:06:13.720 --> 00:06:16.749
a great lifestyle,

00:06:16.759 --> 00:06:19.990
with happiness and abundance.

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:21.710
Money is not supposed to make us happy,

00:06:21.720 --> 00:06:24.589
but it's a lot

00:06:24.599 --> 00:06:25.990
easier to have money than not to have

00:06:25.990 --> 00:06:26.000
it.

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:28.029
That's what I'm believing for

00:06:28.039 --> 00:06:30.550
you today: to be able to say you've got

00:06:30.560 --> 00:06:33.270
enough to help the kingdom of God.

00:06:33.280 --> 00:06:35.950
Father, we thank you and give you praise

00:06:35.960 --> 00:06:39.070
for it.

00:06:39.080 --> 00:06:41.990
Now we believe for our

00:06:41.990 --> 00:06:42.000
bodies—that

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:43.629
we're whole

00:06:43.639 --> 00:06:45.950
spiritually, physically, financially,

00:06:45.960 --> 00:06:48.589
mentally, and emotionally. Father, we pray over

00:06:48.599 --> 00:06:50.629
the bodies, over the health today,

00:06:50.639 --> 00:06:52.710
that they're healed and whole and well

00:06:52.720 --> 00:06:56.110
in the name of Jesus. We speak life over

00:06:56.120 --> 00:06:58.790
their bodies, from the

00:06:58.790 --> 00:06:58.800
top of

00:06:58.800 --> 00:07:01.390
their heads

00:07:01.390 --> 00:07:01.400
to

00:07:01.400 --> 00:07:02.950
the

00:07:02.950 --> 00:07:02.960
soles

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:05.270
of their feet. Lord, we speak life over

00:07:05.280 --> 00:07:07.469
their blood and over their

00:07:07.479 --> 00:07:10.550
cells. No

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:12.909
cancer, no diabetes, and no heart disease

00:07:12.919 --> 00:07:15.150
comes nigh them. Father, I thank you

00:07:15.160 --> 00:07:17.710
that you said in your Word that

00:07:17.720 --> 00:07:19.749
you made them healed by your

00:07:19.759 --> 00:07:22.830
stripes. Thank you, Father, for healing all kinds

00:07:22.840 --> 00:07:25.270
of infections. For somebody, we pray over

00:07:25.280 --> 00:07:27.390
bladder infections and UTIs right now.

00:07:27.400 --> 00:07:29.629
We speak to it, and in the

00:07:29.639 --> 00:07:32.950
name of Jesus, the UTI has to go.

00:07:32.960 --> 00:07:35.550
We speak to prostates to

00:07:35.560 --> 00:07:37.749
be healed and whole in

00:07:37.749 --> 00:07:37.759
Jesus'name.

00:07:37.759 --> 00:07:39.869
Over high blood pressure, we speak

00:07:39.879 --> 00:07:41.830
in the

00:07:41.840 --> 00:07:43.950
name of Jesus. We thank you, Lord,

00:07:43.960 --> 00:07:46.070
that you took all

00:07:46.080 --> 00:07:47.430
those infirmities and bore our

00:07:47.440 --> 00:07:49.510
sicknesses.

00:07:51.520 --> 00:07:53.189
What you bore in your body, we will not

00:07:53.199 --> 00:07:55.469
bear in our body. I thank you

00:07:55.479 --> 00:07:57.589
for your healing power that flows on the

00:07:57.599 --> 00:07:59.869
inside of us. Father, I thank you that you

00:07:59.879 --> 00:08:01.830
put that crown of thorns on for the

00:08:01.830 --> 00:08:01.840
torment—that you took

00:08:01.840 --> 00:08:04.830
any kind

00:08:04.840 --> 00:08:07.510
of mental torment, bad

00:08:07.520 --> 00:08:10.350
dreams, night terrors, or

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:15.670
stress disorders. Father, I thank

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:17.469
you that they're free from those

00:08:17.479 --> 00:08:20.350
things. You said, 'Whom the Son has

00:08:20.360 --> 00:08:22.909
set free is free indeed.'It's been

00:08:22.919 --> 00:08:25.270
on my heart to pray for your finances

00:08:25.270 --> 00:08:25.280
and

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:27.149
for better

00:08:27.149 --> 00:08:27.159
jobs—for

00:08:27.159 --> 00:08:29.749
you to be the head, not the

00:08:29.749 --> 00:08:29.759
tail,

00:08:29.759 --> 00:08:31.469
and above and not beneath. I've

00:08:31.479 --> 00:08:33.389
been stirred about it because I see so

00:08:33.399 --> 00:08:35.949
many people who are lacking.

00:08:35.959 --> 00:08:38.550
It's time to turn

00:08:38.560 --> 00:08:41.909
it around and believe God for

00:08:41.919 --> 00:08:44.389
big. Instead of

00:08:44.389 --> 00:08:44.399
saying, 'I have

00:08:44.399 --> 00:08:47.190
enough for some ramen noodles and

00:08:47.200 --> 00:08:49.190
Beanie Weenies to get

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:51.230
me through the

00:08:51.230 --> 00:08:51.240
week,'you

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:53.470
should be the King's kid eating salmon filets.

00:08:53.470 --> 00:08:53.480
There is

00:08:53.480 --> 00:08:56.350
nothing wrong

00:08:56.360 --> 00:08:58.790
with eating ramen noodles, but I'm

00:08:58.800 --> 00:09:01.750
believing God

00:09:01.750 --> 00:09:01.760
for

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:04.430
overflow

00:09:04.440 --> 00:09:08.750
so

00:09:08.760 --> 00:09:11.750
you can say, 'Lord, thank

00:09:11.760 --> 00:09:15.910
you that the world has our

00:09:15.910 --> 00:09:15.920
stuff.'We're

00:09:15.920 --> 00:09:18.509
tithers, givers, and

00:09:18.509 --> 00:09:18.519
sowers,

00:09:18.519 --> 00:09:20.750
and the wealth of

00:09:20.760 --> 00:09:22.910
the sinner is laid up for the righteous.

00:09:22.920 --> 00:09:25.990
The Lord has me praying

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:28.670
about

00:09:28.670 --> 00:09:28.680
the

00:09:28.680 --> 00:09:30.230
wealth of the sinner's

00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:34.150
hand being laid up for the just.

00:09:34.160 --> 00:09:38.269
The devil's crowd has it,

00:09:38.269 --> 00:09:38.279
but

00:09:38.279 --> 00:09:41.670
we're the King's kids. He has

00:09:41.670 --> 00:09:41.680
the

00:09:41.680 --> 00:09:43.750
cattle on a thousand hills

00:09:43.750 --> 00:09:43.760
and

00:09:43.760 --> 00:09:46.829
overflow in the name of

00:09:46.839 --> 00:09:49.630
Jesus.

00:09:49.640 --> 00:09:52.550
As He is, so are we

00:09:52.560 --> 00:09:56.190
in this world—on earth as it is

00:09:56.200 --> 00:09:58.750
in heaven.

00:09:58.760 --> 00:10:00.750
Because we are flowing in that

00:10:00.760 --> 00:10:03.030
covenant with Him, I'm going to tell

00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:04.630
you: if you have a problem with

00:10:04.640 --> 00:10:06.750
prosperity and

00:10:06.760 --> 00:10:08.509
walking in the blessing, you're

00:10:08.519 --> 00:10:11.590
going to hate heaven.

00:10:11.590 --> 00:10:11.600
From

00:10:11.600 --> 00:10:14.389
what I've seen, even Jesus'crown

00:10:14.389 --> 00:10:14.399
and

00:10:14.399 --> 00:10:16.230
the

00:10:16.230 --> 00:10:16.240
jewels—it's

00:10:16.240 --> 00:10:18.790
beyond anything you can

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:19.990
dare ask or

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:22.470
think. The

00:10:22.480 --> 00:10:24.230
mansions in heaven

00:10:24.230 --> 00:10:24.240
are

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:27.110
overflow.

00:10:31.720 --> 00:10:34.150
There's no poverty in heaven, no

00:10:34.160 --> 00:10:36.230
trailer parks, and no

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:39.069
shacks. There are mansions

00:10:39.069 --> 00:10:39.079
and

00:10:39.079 --> 00:10:41.190
castles; I've seen them,

00:10:41.190 --> 00:10:41.200
and

00:10:41.200 --> 00:10:43.190
they're

00:10:43.200 --> 00:10:45.269
breathtaking.

00:10:48.760 --> 00:10:51.870
The gold is transparent in the

00:10:51.880 --> 00:10:54.230
streets. Like Dorothy in The

00:10:54.240 --> 00:10:56.590
Wizard of Oz,

00:10:56.600 --> 00:10:59.350
follow the Yellow Brick Road.

00:10:59.360 --> 00:11:02.030
This is transparent

00:11:04.480 --> 00:11:07.310
gold; it's so

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:11.470
pure and beautiful.

00:11:11.480 --> 00:11:13.710
If you just took out

00:11:13.720 --> 00:11:15.750
one brick of that street, most people

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:18.030
could live forever off it because

00:11:18.030 --> 00:11:18.040
of

00:11:18.040 --> 00:11:20.069
how pure that gold is.

00:11:21.240 --> 00:11:23.790
I know this is probably getting on some

00:11:23.800 --> 00:11:25.790
people's nerves,

00:11:30.480 --> 00:11:33.829
but the Lord

00:11:33.839 --> 00:11:36.910
wants you blessed.

00:11:40.639 --> 00:11:43.110
I feel it inside to tell you

00:11:43.120 --> 00:11:45.550
today that God wants you to have

00:11:45.560 --> 00:11:47.269
exceedingly abundantly above all you

00:11:47.279 --> 00:11:49.389
dare ask or think. To the tithers and givers

00:11:49.389 --> 00:11:49.399
who

00:11:49.399 --> 00:11:51.389
have sowed and sowed and

00:11:51.399 --> 00:11:54.389
never reaped: it's a spiritual

00:11:54.399 --> 00:11:57.509
law for seed-time and harvest. A lot of

00:11:57.519 --> 00:11:59.790
you believe in sowing, but you don't

00:11:59.800 --> 00:12:01.949
believe in reaping. You push away the

00:12:01.959 --> 00:12:04.110
reaping because it's uncomfortable or you

00:12:04.110 --> 00:12:04.120
feel you should

00:12:04.120 --> 00:12:06.670
just

00:12:06.670 --> 00:12:06.680
be

00:12:06.680 --> 00:12:08.509
humble.

00:12:14.839 --> 00:12:17.710
God will build the character in you

00:12:17.720 --> 00:12:21.030
so money won't destroy

00:12:21.030 --> 00:12:21.040
you.

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:23.389
He's

00:12:23.399 --> 00:12:26.470
a

00:12:26.480 --> 00:12:28.509
God

00:12:28.519 --> 00:12:30.550
of

00:12:30.560 --> 00:12:33.430
love. I hope this video blessed

00:12:33.430 --> 00:12:33.440
you

00:12:33.440 --> 00:12:35.790
all today.

00:12:44.880 --> 00:12:48.310
Stop thinking small and

00:12:48.320 --> 00:12:51.430
believe God bigger. He is a big God, and

00:12:51.440 --> 00:12:53.910
if the devil's crowd can have it, we

00:12:53.920 --> 00:12:55.790
should take it. It's

00:12:55.800 --> 00:12:59.389
time to plunder hell and

00:12:59.399 --> 00:13:01.870
populate heaven and take authority

00:13:01.880 --> 00:13:04.870
over the devil.

00:13:18.800 --> 00:13:21.470
He gave you

00:13:21.480 --> 00:13:25.310
dominion.

00:13:25.320 --> 00:13:28.150
Whatsoever things you bind on

00:13:28.160 --> 00:13:29.790
earth will be bound in heaven, and whatsoever

00:13:29.800 --> 00:13:31.509
things you loose on earth will be

00:13:31.509 --> 00:13:31.519
loosed

00:13:31.519 --> 00:13:32.829
in heaven.

00:13:36.240 --> 00:13:38.710
He said whatsoever things *you*

00:13:38.720 --> 00:13:40.870
say out of your mouth and believe

00:13:40.880 --> 00:13:44.230
in your heart will come to pass.

00:13:44.240 --> 00:13:46.030
Expectation brings

00:13:46.040 --> 00:13:49.590
manifestation.

00:13:49.600 --> 00:13:51.949
I thank you, Father,

00:13:51.959 --> 00:13:53.870
that it's coming to pass.

00:13:53.880 --> 00:13:55.670
The seeds we sowed in

00:13:55.680 --> 00:13:58.710
the past will come to harvest at last in

00:13:58.720 --> 00:14:00.470
the name of

00:14:00.480 --> 00:14:05.310
Jesus. Amen and amen and amen.

